	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salus et pax Christi.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">28. iunii<note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a"><hi>in der Vorlage</hi> iunii.</note> abiit <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Ambrosius</persName> <placeName ref="l18" cert="high">Augustam</placeName><note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1"><persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Ambrosius Blarer</persName> reiste am 18.(!) Juni nach <placeName ref="l18" cert="high">Augsburg</placeName> ab (vgl. oben <ref target="file11324">Nr. 1281</ref>, 72-74), wo er am 27. Juni eintraf (s. <hi>Roth</hi> II 441). Der <placeName ref="l18" cert="high">Augsburger</placeName> Rat hatte ihn gebeten, an der Befriedung der zerstrittenen Kirche mitzuwirken; s. <hi>Roth</hi> II 440-449.</note> comite domino et angelis eius; hunc commendo orationibus tuis.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Miserat autem, priusquam abiret, <persName ref="p1365" cert="high">Grynęo</persName> scriptum nostrum, quod de conventu <placeName ref="l361" cert="high">Norimbergensi</placeName> senatui nostro obtulimus<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Zum Gutachten der <placeName ref="l257" cert="high">Konstanzer</placeName> Theologen über das geplante Religionsgespräch s. oben <ref target="file11324">Nr. 1281</ref>, 49-51 mit Anm. 12, und <ref target="file11325">Nr. 1282</ref>, 2-13.</note>.<pb type="edition" next="175"/></s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nunc optimus vir <persName ref="p1365" cert="high">Grynęus</persName> scribit ad nos <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8055" cert="high">Blaureros</persName> et <persName type="citizen_name" cert="high" ref="p4079">Zviccios</persName> bene longam epistolam<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3"><persName ref="p1365" cert="high">Grynäus</persName>' Brief an die Gebrüder <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Blarer</persName> und <persName ref="p4079" cert="high">Zwick</persName> ist nicht erhalten.</note>, in qua confutat nostram sententiam, sed multa synceritate et charitate; meliora enim sperat, quam nos vaticinemur.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed et nos optamus irritari nostra vaticinia, magis vero conventum ipsum irritari optamus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Iamque omnino nichil audimus et silent omnia, sed fiat, quod domino placuerit.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Mitto hic tibi libellum <persName ref="p1974" cert="high">Lutheri</persName><note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4">Gemeint ist <persName ref="p1974" cert="high">Luthers</persName> Schrift "Von den Konziliis und Kirchen" (<bibl>WA</bibl> L 488-653); vgl. unten <ref target="file11332">Nr. 1289</ref>, 1-5 sowie <persName ref="p8049" cert="high">Vadian</persName> BW V 565.</note> apertum et candidum, quem communicabis <persName ref="p8127" cert="high">Pellicano</persName>, <persName ref="p1753" cert="high">Leoni</persName><note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5"><persName ref="p1753" cert="high">Leo Jud</persName>.</note>, <persName ref="p8171" cert="high">Theodoro</persName><note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6"><persName ref="p8171" cert="high">Theodor Bibliander</persName>.</note> et reliquis.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Proinde conclusiones quasdam<note xml:id="fn7" type="footnote" n="7">Wohl <persName ref="p1974" cert="high">Luthers</persName> Thesen zur Frage des Widerstands gegen den Kaiser vom April 1539, die u. a. in Basel nachgedruckt wurden (<bibl>WA</bibl> XXXIX/II 34-51).</note> mitto, sed eas omnino remittendas; non enim meae sunt.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Utinam vero apud vos imprimerentur!</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Praeterea haud ita pridem scripsi ad te<note xml:id="fn8" type="footnote" n="8">Ein entsprechendes Schreiben ist nicht erhalten.</note>, ut me certiorem faceres, si quis apud vos iuvenis, qui mihi amanuensis loco esse posset quique nonnunquam hypodidascalum agere posset in scola.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Neque vero mittendus est statim,<pb type="scan" next="58"/> sed describendus.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ea in re <persName ref="p8127" cert="high">Pellicani</persName> operam cumprimis desydero; nam ille meum quoque ingenium satis novit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Valete omnes in domino incolumes.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Datum 5. iulii 1539.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName ref="p4079" cert="high">Io. Zvick</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf f. 58a v.:]</note>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Domino <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Hainricho Bullingero</persName>, fratri meo in domino charissimo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
